org.apache.hadoop.hbase.chaos.factories

Class DistributedIssuesMonkeyFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.chaos.factories.MonkeyFactory
      • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.chaos.factories.DistributedIssuesMonkeyFactory

  • public class DistributedIssuesMonkeyFactory
extends MonkeyFactory
    A chaos monkey to create distributed cluster related issues, requires a user with passwordless ssh access to the cluster and sudo privileges.
